    pc "Ah oui ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:27
translate french danamoviedate_feedb9ad:

    # cw "Oh yeah. I've been thinking about your dick all day."
    cw "Oh oui. J'ai pensé à ta bite toute la journée."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:29
translate french danamoviedate_30143840:

    # cw "But I also really want to see this movie, so even if it's bad, you have to be a good boyfriend and watch it with me."
    cw "Mais j'ai aussi vraiment envie de voir ce film, donc même s'il est nul, tu dois être un bon petit ami et le regarder avec moi."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:30
translate french danamoviedate_2c438d9a:

    # pc "I guess I can do that."
    pc "Je suppose que je peux faire ça."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:31
translate french danamoviedate_3196ae44:

    # "We chat for a bit before the movie starts."
    "On discute un peu avant que le film commence."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:37
translate french danamoviedate_8de46db7:

    # "Then the theater goes dark and everybody quiets down."
    "Puis la salle s'assombrit et tout le monde se tait."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:42
translate french danamoviedate_8ec143f8:

    # "We watch the movie together. It's cheesy, but isn't too bad."
    "On regarde le film ensemble. C'est un peu ringard, mais ce n'est pas trop mal."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:43
translate french danamoviedate_954db5c8:

    # "And Dana laughs a lot during it, which is nice."
    "Et Dana rit beaucoup pendant le film, ce qui est sympa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:48
translate french danamoviedate_2a9c215f:

    # "Towards the end of the movie, she leans over onto my shoulder and I put my arm around her."
    "Vers la fin du film, elle se penche sur mon épaule et je passe mon bras autour d'elle."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danamoviedate.rpy:49
translate french danamoviedate_54e4c6ed:

